<html
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
  xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
  xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
  xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
  xml:lang="en"
  lang="en"
  dir="ltr"
  metal:use-macro="view/macro:page/onecolumn"
  i18n:domain="launchpad"
>
<body>

<div metal:fill-slot="main">

  <h1>Translations settings</h1>

  <p
    class="not-translated-in-launchpad"
    tal:condition="not: context/product/official_rosetta">

    <strong>
      This project is not configured to use Launchpad for translations.
    </strong>
    <tal:admin_or_owner condition="context/product/required:launchpad.Edit">
      You can change this in the
      <a tal:attributes="href string:${context/product/fmt:url}/+edit">
        project settings</a>.
    </tal:admin_or_owner>
  </p>
  <p>
    You can let Launchpad automatically import your translation 
    templates (.pot files) from the
    bazaar branch hosted on Launchpad that is associated with
    <strong tal:content="view/context/title">Evolution Series:trunk</strong>.
    The current setting is:<br />
  </p>
  <p tal:condition="view/context/branch"><code
         tal:content="view/context/branch/displayname">
    lp:~/branch/url</code></p>
  <p tal:condition="not:view/context/branch">No Launchpad hosted 
    branch is associated with this series.</p>
  <div metal:use-macro="context/@@launchpad_form/form" />
</div>

</body>
</html>
